  mutate(abs_error = abs(medv-Y_hat))

  geom_histogram(aes(abs_error), bins = 60) +
  theme_light() +
  ggtitle("Histogram of Absolut Error") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5)) +
